const AirportStatistics = ({ statistics }) => { const { averageElevation, noIataCount, noIataAirports, topTimezones, elevationPerCountry, } = statistics return (

Airport Statistics

{/* Average Elevation */}

Average Elevation

{averageElevation} ft

{/* No IATA Codes */}

Airports without IATA

{noIataCount} ( {Math.round( (noIataCount / (noIataCount + (topTimezones.reduce((acc, tz) => acc + tz.count, 0) - noIataCount))) * 100, )} %)

    {noIataAirports && noIataAirports.map((airport) => (
  • {airport.name}
    • ))}
{/* Top Timezones */}

Top Timezones

    {topTimezones.map((tz) => (
  • {tz.timezone} {tz.count}
    • ))}
{/* Average Elevation per Country */}

Avg Elevation per Country

    {elevationPerCountry.map((country) => (
  • {country.country} {country.average} ft
    • ))}
) } export default AirportStatistics
